# Syncthing

## Safety marker - DO NOT DELETE. 
## If this is missing, Syncthing stops to prevent data loss.
.stfolder

## Trash Can / Versioning folder. 
## Safe to ignore if you don't want to sync deleted files to other devices.
.stversions

## The ignore file itself.
## Adding this prevents the ignore rules from syncing to other devices.
.stignore

